      "title": "Man arrested for hoarding Diesel",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); An individual was arrested in Vanathawilluwa for hoarding fuel to be sold for exorbitant prices.",
        "Sri Lanka Police seized around 300 liters of Diesel concealed in the house in Wanathawilluwa.",
        "The detainee is to be presented to the Puttalam Magistrate Court."
